==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slot machine
<hw>Slot" ma*chine"</hw>. <def>A machine the operation of which is
started by dropping a coin into a slot, for delivering small articles of
merchandise, showing one's weight, exhibiting pictures, throwing dice,
gambling, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slotted</ent>⟦br⟧
